data.description: Adorable 2 Bedroom Cabin In Idyllwild.  Vaulted ceilings, woodstove, dual pane windows, indoor laundry, and pantry.  Large kitchen with great appliances and central heating.  This home features sprawling decks with great views and a large horseshoe driveway with extra parking.  Located 5 minutes from downtown and very close to hiking trails this mountain home is a must see!
